      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854307,
      "updated": 1781856911
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f06b00000000000bb902",
      "text": "\t\t[[https://gyazo.com/56a831ee57637bf9cf82e245cef1fd62]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854316,
      "updated": 1781857082
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34fa96000000000081652f",
      "text": "\t\t[[https://gyazo.com/df439d59de54547d4c60d68500ab33bf]]",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781856918,
      "updated": 1781857095
    },
    {
      "id": "6a35023f000000000042d25f",
      "text": "  スタイルは揃っていると感じるが、個人的には細い線（最初のバージョン）で揃える方が好きかも[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781858880,
      "updated": 1781930842
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361ba6000000000074cbdd",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/037a749eea2468dd2be8e87a1d99300f]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930916,
      "updated": 1781930917
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361b26000000000074cbdb",
      "text": "   細いほうがスタイリッシュな感じがする",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930788,
      "updated": 1781930926
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361b2b000000000074cbdc",
      "text": "   変更範囲が既存記法にまで及んでいる気持ち悪さがある",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930793,
      "updated": 1781930858
    },
    {
      "id": "6a368a4e00000000005acd2a",
      "text": "   　わかる[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781959247,
      "updated": 1781959266
    },
    {
      "id": "6a361bbe000000000074cbdf",
      "text": "   色の調整もされているんだな",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1781930940,
      "updated": 1781930994
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d9d900000000003d3f7a",
      "text": "   線を1pxにすると配色が判別しづらくなる問題がありまして…[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781979610,
      "updated": 1782121134
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3688a800000000005acd25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781958825,
      "updated": 1782120388
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36974500000000005acd44",
      "text": "斜体式",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781962566,
      "updated": 1782124737
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3708060000000000cd34c2",
      "text": "　[インライン引用記法#61fe2ef67838e3000051f6b3]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781991431,
      "updated": 1782124738
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36974500000000005acd45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781962566,
      "updated": 1781962566
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39069600000000002d7a3b",
      "text": "引用符アイコンと下線の案（河川敷）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122134,
      "updated": 1782123388
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3906ce00000000002d7a3c",
      "text": " [Nrem.icon]がゴリ押し🦍しようとしている案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122190,
      "updated": 1782124719
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39127200000000008f019e",
      "text": " 　反対意見多数なら差し戻します",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782125171,
      "updated": 1782125205
    },
    {
      "id": "6a376eb10000000000f8f03f",
      "text": "　もう何も分からない。おれたちは雰囲気でスタイリングしている",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782017714,
      "updated": 1782130910
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3901b100000000002d7a29",
      "text": "　　逆か。[抽象化]して再構築した結果が人からのフィードバックと必ずしも一致しない",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120881,
      "updated": 1782123469
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39069400000000002d7a3a",
      "text": "下線式の設計思想",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122132,
      "updated": 1782124806
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd03",
      "text": " table:引用ブロックとインライン引用の対照表",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120222,
      "updated": 1782120437
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff2a0000000000bb8216",
      "text": " 　\t引用ブロック記法（変更後）\tインライン引用記法（下線式）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120234,
      "updated": 1782122678
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff2a0000000000bb8217",
      "text": " 　書式の対象\t行全体\t行の一部（インライン要素）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120234,
      "updated": 1782120395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff2a0000000000bb8218",
      "text": " 　スケール感\tひとまとまり\t部分的、局所的、文の一部",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120234,
      "updated": 1782120395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff2a0000000000bb8219",
      "text": " 　引用の基本単位\t文章。一行から複数の段落\t一語句、一節、一段落",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120234,
      "updated": 1782120395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff2a0000000000bb821a",
      "text": " 　\t\t（直接の言及箇所をピンポイントで提示する使用法が多い）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120234,
      "updated": 1782159995
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd08",
      "text": " 　font\tnormal (default)\tsmaller (BIZ UDゴシック / weight 400 - 450) ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1782120405
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd09",
      "text": " 　マーカー\t行頭の区切り線（左側）/中程度の太さ\t下線/細め × 引用符アイコン",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1782121808
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39009d00000000002d7a18",
      "text": " 　\t（想定値 3px - 3.5px 程度）\t（想定幅 2px - 2.5px）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120605,
      "updated": 1782120631
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39008300000000002d7a13",
      "text": " \t\t背景色\t背景色、小さめの文字サイズ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120579,
      "updated": 1782120675
    },
    {
      "id": "6a367f7500000000005acd0a",
      "text": " 　余白\t字下げによる余白\t引用符アイコンの領域（左端）、通常テキストとの境界（左右端）",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781956470,
      "updated": 1782123672
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39014100000000002d7a26",
      "text": " 　\t行末全体に偏在（右側）\tテキストの上側",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120769,
      "updated": 1782128204
    },
    {
      "id": "6a38ff510000000000bb8220",
      "text": " 　導線、重心\t行頭の区切り線（左側） / 左寄せ\t段落の baseline（下方向） / テキストの流れる方向",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782120273,
      "updated": 1782123678
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d5ad00000000003d3f70",
      "text": " 基本的な考え方",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978542,
      "updated": 1782124608
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36d5ad00000000003d3f71",
      "text": " 　`引用ブロックのスケール感 > インライン引用のスケール感`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781978542,
      "updated": 1782120395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a390c120000000000387fcb",
      "text": " 寸法の相関関係",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782123540,
      "updated": 1782130885
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3928c100000000000c1531",
      "text": " 　`上側のpadding > 引用符アイコン ≈ border-bottom + padding-bottom ≈ 左右のpadding`",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782130882,
      "updated": 1782131818
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39290d00000000000c1534",
      "text": " インライン引用記法の下線について",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782130958,
      "updated": 1782160559
    },
    {
      "id": "6a392a3600000000000c1538",
      "text": " 　`border:`の明度コントラストが文字色に近いほど「強調」の意味合いに近づく",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782131255,
      "updated": 1782160580
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39298400000000000c1536",
      "text": " 　`border-bottom:`（下線）は、テキストと同じレイヤーというより背景色の領域の一部分として提示される必要がある。背景色とのコントラストが肝要",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782131078,
      "updated": 1782160545
    },
    {
      "id": "6a392a9a00000000000c1539",
      "text": " 　　1px（Cosenseの引用ブロックの境界線）では面積が零に近しいため、`background-color:`と分離するためのコントラストの下限が高くなる",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782131355,
      "updated": 1782160423
    },
    {
      "id": "6a399ab100000000008901f5",
      "text": " 　　　引用ブロックとインライン引用に同じ配色を適用しつつ、インライン引用の「下線」のコントラストを下げるには、引用ブロック側の `border-width:`も変更する必要がある",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782160050,
      "updated": 1782160616
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39291600000000000c1535",
      "text": " 　インライン引用記法の具体的な使われ方のうち、「直接の言及箇所を提示する」使用法は既知の下線の用法と類似性や親和性があるのではないか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782130967,
      "updated": 1782159629
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3928c500000000000c1532",
      "text": " ほか",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782130887,
      "updated": 1782130889
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3928ca00000000000c1533",
      "text": " 　[/nrem-configs/インライン引用記法のデザインの違いと心理的影響]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782130891,
      "updated": 1782130893
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39067d00000000002d7a38",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122109,
      "updated": 1782122109
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39066700000000002d7a36",
      "text": "開始引用符＋終了引用符案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122087,
      "updated": 1782122254
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39071000000000002d7a3d",
      "text": "　",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122256,
      "updated": 1782122257
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39066600000000002d7a35",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122086,
      "updated": 1782122086
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39060600000000002d7a31",
      "text": "Cosenseの引用ブロックをそのままインライン引用にする案",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782121990,
      "updated": 1782122018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39062400000000002d7a32",
      "text": "　[caki.icon]のジャストアイデア",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122020,
      "updated": 1782124678
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907590000000000387fbe",
      "text": "　次のUserCSSは[Nrem.icon]による試作品",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122331,
      "updated": 1782122561
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907f50000000000387fc0",
      "text": "　　[https://gyazo.com/96f5ddb0c4c457bb2b11ad74f92f79c7][https://gyazo.com/408eb73fd7a333bdb8c4934d92fa8cd6]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122486,
      "updated": 1782122574
    },
    {
      "id": "6a390a8f0000000000387fca",
      "text": "　　まだ試行錯誤の段階で、border が少し太めの状態となっています",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782123152,
      "updated": 1782159681
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39063600000000002d7a33",
      "text": " 　code:blockquote-to-inline-quote.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122038,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a39065e00000000002d7a34",
      "text": " 　 .line .deco-\\\" {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122078,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fae",
      "text": "   \tdisplay: inline;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387faf",
      "text": "   \tborder: none, none, none, none !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb0",
      "text": "   \tborder-bottom: none;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb1",
      "text": "   \tborder-left: solid 1px #a0a0a0;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb2",
      "text": "   \tpadding-left: 2.5px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb3",
      "text": "   \tpadding-right: 3px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb4",
      "text": "   \tpadding-top: 5px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb5",
      "text": "   \tpadding-bottom: 5px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb6",
      "text": "   \tbackground-color: var(--quote-bg-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb7",
      "text": "   \tcolor: var(--quote-text-color, var(--page-text-color));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb8",
      "text": "   \tfont-size: 0.9em;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fb9",
      "text": "   \ttext-align: unset;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fba",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fbb",
      "text": "   .line .deco-\\\"::before {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fbc",
      "text": "   \tdisplay: none !important;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3907500000000000387fbd",
      "text": "   }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782122321,
      "updated": 1782122417
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3902fd00000000002d7a2b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782121213,
      "updated": 1782121213
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3902fd00000000002d7a2c",
      "text": "[稲妻形引用ブロック]というものがあるらしい。少し気になります[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1782121213,
      "updated": 1782121986
    },
    {
      "id": "6a3717550000000000cf8b71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781995350,
      "updated": 1781995350
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bb1300000000001ec60c",
      "text": "[引用記法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971732,
      "updated": 1781971742
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec600",
      "text": " code:2026-06-19-1.css",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971706
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec601",
      "text": "  html {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec602",
      "text": "   \t--quote-border-color: light-dark(hsl(216 10% 75%), hsl(196 10% 43%));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec603",
      "text": "  \t--quote-border-width: 3.5px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec604",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-border-width: 2px;",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec605",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec606",
      "text": "  .line .quote {",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec607",
      "text": "  \tborder-left: solid var(--quote-border-width, 1px)  var(--quote-border-color, #a0a0a0);",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec608",
      "text": "  \tbackground-color: var(--quote-bg-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bae300000000001ec609",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971684,
      "updated": 1781971684
    },
    {
      "id": "6a36bb0200000000001ec60a",
      "text": "[インライン引用記法]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1781971715,
      "updated": 1781971726
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f00a00000000000bb8fb",
      "text": "\tcode:2026-06-19-1.css",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854267,
      "updated": 1781858880
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f01700000000000bb8fc",
      "text": "\t\t@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=BIZ+UDGothic:wght@400;700&display=swap');",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854267,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90b",
      "text": "  html {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90c",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-font-family: \"Roboto\", Helvetica, Arial, \"BIZ UDゴシック\", \"BIZ UDGothic\", \"Hiragino Sans\";",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90d",
      "text": "  \t--inline-quote-font-size-adjust: 0.51;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90e",
      "text": "  }",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb90f",
      "text": "  .deco-\\\" {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb910",
      "text": "  \t.line & {",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb911",
      "text": "  \t\tvertical-align: baseline;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb912",
      "text": "  \t\tbox-sizing: content-box; /* padding: 5.5px 4.5px 0.5px 2px; */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb913",
      "text": "  \t\tpadding: 5.5px 4px 1px 2px;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb914",
      "text": "  \t\tborder-bottom: solid var(--inline-quote-border-width, var(--quote-border-width, 1px)) var(--quote-border-color, #a0a0a0);",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb915",
      "text": "   \t\tbackground-color: var(--quote-bg-color, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05));",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb916",
      "text": "  \t\tcolor: var(--quote-text-color, var(--page-text-color, inherit));",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb917",
      "text": "  \t\tfont-size: .94em;",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb918",
      "text": "   \t\t/* font-weight: var(--inline-quote-font-weight, var(--quote-font-weight, 450)); */",
      "userId": "5ffbd8b8512f4e001cae68fd",
      "created": 1781854490,
      "updated": 1781854490
    },
    {
      "id": "6a34f11a00000000000bb919",
